    items: [
      {
        q: "What is ISO 27002?",
        a: "ISO 27002 is an internationally recognized standard that provides guidelines for selecting, implementing, and managing information security controls. It supports the requirements of ISO 27001 by offering best practices and detailed guidance for each control, helping organizations protect their information assets.",
      },
      {
        q: "Who should use ISO 27002?",
