      },
      {
        q: "What are the main domains covered by ISO 27002?",
        a: "ISO 27002 organizes controls into domains such as organizational controls, people controls, physical controls, and technological controls. Each domain addresses different aspects of information security, from policy management to technical safeguards.",
      },
